  "body": "See https://github.com/NomicFoundation/hardhat/pull/4574 and https://github.com/NomicFoundation/hardhat/issues/4190 for extra context.\r\n\r\nRight now we rely on `eth_feeHistory`, and only use `eth_maxPriorityFeePerGas` when the estimated max priority fee is 0. This doesn't seem ideal. We should re-visit our algorithm and see how it can be improved. For example, maybe we can use `eth_feeHistory` only for the max fee and `eth_maxPriorityFeePerGas` for the max priority fee. But we need to be careful since one of the methods, or both, could not exist.",
